<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>jiabeng</title>
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="../img/apple-touch-icon.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="../img/favicon-32x32.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="../img/favicon-16x16.png">
	<link rel="manifest" href="../img/manifest.json">
	<link rel="mask-icon" href="../img/safari-pinned-tab.svg" color="#5bbad5">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/info_page_style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="profile">
    	<img src="../<%= content["profile_img"]%>" alt="">
    </div>
	<div class="container">
      <div class="left">
        <div class="top">
          <div class="icon">
          <img src="http://i.imgur.com/XVa8hVK.png" width="120" height="100">
          </div>

          <div class="title">
          <h1><%= content["title"] %></h1>
          </div>
	</div>

        <BR></BR>

        <div class="down">
          <div class="food-picture">
          <img src="../<%= content["img_url"] %>" width="400" height="300">
          </div>
        </div>
     </div>

     <div class="right">

        <div class="descriptions">
        	<div class="sources">
        		<h2>食材：</h2>
           		<h3><%=content["materials"]%></h2>
        	</div>
        	<div id="price">
        		<h2 >價格：</h2>
           		<h3>$<%= content["price"] %>元/份</h2>
        	</div>
        	<div id="place">
        		<h2>地點：</h2>
           		<h3>臺南市東區大學路1號</h2>
        	</div>
          	<div id="time">
        		<h2>時間：</h2>
           		<h3>15:00~18:00</h2>
        	</div>
        	<div id="introduction">
        		<h2>介紹:</h2>
        		<div id="content">
        			日本料理太保守`封閉又缺乏包容力·甚至很少使用新食材；其次，烹調時必須使用軟水和好的漁獲，否則無法呈現應有的水準，因此很難推廣至國際
        		</div>
        	</div>
        </div>
        <a href="/trade/<%=content["id"]%>"><button id = "submit">我要吃</button><a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>